Manufacturing Work Instructions

Document ID: WI-2024-089
Revision: C
Effective Date: 2024-12-01

Part Number: MP-450-X
Part Description: Motor Mount Plate

Required Tools:
- CNC Mill
- 1/4" End Mill
- Drill Press
- Deburring Tool
- Calipers (0.001" resolution)

Process Steps:
--------------

1. SETUP
   - Verify material: 0.250" Aluminum 6061-T6 plate
   - Check material certification
   - Clean workpiece surface

2. MACHINING
   - Face both sides to 0.245" +/- 0.002"
   - Mill perimeter to dimensions per blueprint
   - Drill mounting holes: (4x) 0.257" dia
   - Tap holes: (4x) 1/4-20 UNC, minimum 0.5" depth

3. FINISHING
   - Deburr all edges
   - Remove sharp corners (0.020" radius)
   - Clean with solvent

4. INSPECTION
   - Verify all dimensions per blueprint
   - Check thread engagement with gauge
   - Visual inspection for defects

5. MARKING
   - Stamp part number on back side
   - Mark with revision level

